comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-04T17:53:32.045Z",codex-agent,Duplicate-check evidence pm context --limit 10; pm search validate check-files missing_linked_paths false positive --limit 20; pm list-open --limit 20; pm list-in-progress --limit 20. Net-new because no existing item tracks this active false-positive behavior.
  "2026-04-04T17:54:15.825Z",codex-agent,"Reproduction captured after governance remediation: pm validate --check-files --scan-mode tracked-all still reports 9 missing_linked_paths even after explicit linking. Independent audit (git tracked minus parsed project file links) reports candidate=202 linked=222 missing=0, confirming false-positive behavior in validate path matching layer."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-04T17:53:32.045Z",codex-agent,Independent git-vs-linked audit currently reports candidate=202 linked=222 missing=0 while validate reports 9 missing paths.
